### Altium Designer ###

# Thumbnail and preview cache — auto-generated, large binary blobs
**/__Previews/

# Local version history — managed by Altium 365, not needed in git
**/History/

# Project logs
Project Logs*/

# Auto-generated project structure file (Altium 365 cloud sync metadata)
# Note: both case variants listed — Linux git is case-sensitive
*.PrjPcbStructure
*.PrjPCBStructure
*.PrjMbdStructure

# HTML auto-conversion notice files
*.PcbDoc.htm
*.SchDoc.htm

# Database link lock files
**/*.ldb

# Local document metadata (Altium 365 local state)
*.metadata

# CompareHistory folder
CompareHistory/

# CAMtastic files — regeneratable from Gerbers, large binary
*.CAM
*.Cam

# Built-in Altium integrated libraries — do not redistribute (Altium license)
Miscellaneous Devices.IntLib
Miscellaneous Connectors.IntLib

